        "subject": "LU-5459 lov: adjust page bufsize after layout change",
        "message": "LU-5459 lov: adjust page bufsize after layout change\n\nOtherwise, the coh_page_bufsize keeps increasing when the file's\nlayout keeps changing in lov_init_raid0().\n\nThis is a backport to b2_5 from\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/11394/3\nLustre-commit: df9bfaf3b48124e201cbea845b0aac5a8aad8b7d\n\nTo make this work, the lov_page_slice_fixup() routine was\ntaken and incorporated from\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7895\nLustre-commit: 18834a5554f2a5a8615f259be48bb2df9101b5a2\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I70066b916d72aabe0349a1faec65eff160e9cf04\nReviewed-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\nReviewed-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam@gmail.com>\nReviewed-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
      },
